{
  "stem": "27335.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, when it came day-- daylight, then I walked into-- into town, not very far, about five minutes walk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I just stood on one side of street and was waiting for-- for Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Zolo who had this-- this electric-- electric store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when-- when he opened up the store, I waited a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then a few customers went in there with a couple of-- an old peasant women came in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went and looked around when-- when the-- the woman went out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I just-- just turned-- I turned around, you see, and that, he-- he coming to-- to speak to you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, two-- two [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Aerocross ?] soldier and a civilian in between them stepped right into the door-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Zolo, you are under arrest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I just sneaked out right-- right-- right-- right by them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was-- he was under arrest, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, he was-- he was a Jew, and-- and probably suspected that he was-- he was with the partisans, because when he was coming, and he-- he linked-- linked me up with the partisans there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And well, that was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was going to go to-- to that farm where I came in, to that direction.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then, I took off walking from there, towards the place where I-- I-- I-- in the-- that direction where I-- I came in, wanted to reach that-- that peasant-- that peasant [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, and in that direction, I was-- I was about two kilometers away from the border already, the Slovak border there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was the border guards there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I looked around-- I looked around left and right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Walking out there, I went through, luckily, the cornfields, and so to-- to-- to hide myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
